-- MOVES-Mayank Parekh joins Value Partners from McKinsey
-- By Rishika Sadam in Bangalore
-- Tue Oct 28, 2014 02:28AM EDT
-- None



Oct 28 (Reuters) - Value Partners appointed Mayank Parekh as director and managing partner for Asia and Demetrio Di Martino to lead telecom media technology (TMT) practice in Asia.

The management consultancy also named Yeo Soo Ruey to lead its Asia-wide private equity practice. Parekh, who was formerly a partner with McKinsey & Co, will focus on the firm's business strategy for the region.